EFL Jose's Cup of tea Jose Mourinho up for the cup: Manchester United boss admits he learnt the hard way about disrespecting the FA Cup at Newcastle 12 years ago 
Mourinho's weakened Chelsea side were knocked out at St James' Park and the Special One has always played strong teams since By NEIL CUSTIS
